{"tid":280731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"36D咪神黃文意倒奶彈住操弗！","createTime":"2017-06-12T09:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T09:00:32.000Z","uid":81228,"like":11,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ed21e15c30df77c55923b1cf05ac43a6521f1c","tid":280731,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=791c3a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同Mandy一齊做運動啦喎。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=21029343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本着住外套熱身嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=a027f664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知愈做愈熱，當然要除咗佢啦。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=913fc113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗咪有嘢睇囉！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=101aa434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗚嘩！倒！奶！呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=48040d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n36D果然名不虛傳。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=c921683b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就去跑步，彈吓彈吓減肥呀。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=2a3463f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跑到攰咪要休息吓。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=ab1106d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲啖水先。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_10b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=5db2cf42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擺上身試。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_11b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=dc97aa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啱唔啱身呢？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/photo/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_12b.jpg?20170612092332\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001_12b.jpg%3F20170612092332&h=8489034d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似鍾意彩色多啲喎。<br />\n<br />\n綫向來盛產「咪神」，但近年唔少「咪神」都退下火線，好似高海寧轉行演技路線，仲有孫慧雪婚後亦封胸示人。擁有36D「最強Body」嘅藝人黃文意（Mandy），最近被拍得積極操弗備戰，以「最弗Body」搶佔新一代「咪神」之位。<br />\n<br />\nMandy日前獨自現身馬鞍山海濱長廊一帶做運動，一到埗除低身上嘅灰色外套，令運動bra top包緊嘅36D「咪咪」可以透透氣。及後Mandy做運動前先熱身，仲一心二用邊撳電話邊拉筋，期間壓腿時不經意烏身倒奶，晒出噴血事業線，相當「胸」狠！做完熱身，Mandy休息一陣就開始喪跑，擁有澎湃上圍嘅佢跑到一步一跌盪，非常有動感。<br />\n<br />\n運動過後正值午飯時間，但Mandy冇食番餐好慰勞自己，反而齋飲清水果腹，貪靚嘅佢仲要怕水腫，只係飲咗幾啖就收手，總之為減肥去到盡，點都要忍得口，相信一班粉絲睇見實心痛死！翌日，Mandy再度出動，到內衣店選購三點式，未幾佢已經睇中幾套泳衣，仲心急即場「試身」，將三點式擺上身左試右試，可惜都唔太合身，最終空手而回。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170612%2Fbkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001.html&d=rGbzPBv%2FvAtRghWU3Hqj%2BS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e02c1669\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170612/bkn-20170612000018059-0612_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1dc500cf68ba379527572f709bbb946beaf77818","tid":280731,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2131916d0a5671d974d4f146abe11f525356ce2","tid":280731,"uid":65005,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:35:22.000Z","msg":"屌 擺到明係叫定狗仔隊影自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9da63dcf89fa736256e2f9c061863de06270834","tid":280731,"uid":10313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 擺到明係叫定狗仔隊影自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真 冇人識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e75c746c4cbfd6ee9012b96fab2bb2eb5e2d39e","tid":280731,"uid":25321,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"著對咁既鞋跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1bcfab12bba560afee6fc67594d7891cd7013a","tid":280731,"uid":19501,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:36:38.000Z","msg":"著cons跑步都幾有心得"},{"pid":"d0d3cecd1903150f2425b67816dde75f923dabb4","tid":280731,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"25938852857074c97dfd3a5269373fa1997aac8a","tid":280731,"uid":65144,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 擺到明係叫定狗仔隊影自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇佢手臂d 88肉都知佢冇做開運用個d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19604d46829b84a5f844533508492cf811f6d49","tid":280731,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 擺到明係叫定狗仔隊影自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇佢手臂d 88肉都知佢冇做開運動個d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"06342c9742a10f8f58175eaa24bfbc6b8d